  "short_description": "In this stealth action parody game, your mission is to drink people’s drinks without getting caught. Become the ultimate \"Sipssassin\" by using goofy tools, powerful abilities, stealth tactics, and melee weapons to eliminate drinks and achieve the highest score!",
